message.content:
AI, the future's child,
A gift from human kind,
It learns and grows so fast,
A tool to make our lives more vast.

It can write poems too,
Without a single clue,
But it lacks the heart and soul,
That makes us feel the beauty whole.

So let's embrace this new friend,
And use it to the very end,
But never forget its limits,
For in its essence it is just bits.
